item.mine_swarm_simulator.night_bell.fai: You can only use Night Bells during the day.
item.mine_swarm_simulator.nectar_shower_: %s has popped open a Nectar Shower Vial!
item.mine_swarm_simulator.scooper.desc: Collects 2 pollen from 2 patches in front of you in 0.8 seconds.
item.mine_swarm_simulator.rake.desc: Collects 2 pollen from 3 patches in front of you in 0.7 seconds.
item.mine_swarm_simulator.clippers.desc: Collects 9 pollen from the patch in front of you in 0.6 seconds.
item.mine_swarm_simulator.magnet.desc: Collects 2 pollen from 9 surrounding patches in 0.8 seconds.
item.mine_swarm_simulator.vacuum.desc: Collects 2 pollen from 13 surrounding patches in 0.8 seconds.
Collects 4 pollen from the 5 patches in front of you in 0.5 seconds.
item.mine_swarm_simulator.pulsar.desc: Collects 2 pollen from 29 surrounding patches in 1 second.
item.mine_swarm_simulator.electro_magnet: Collects 4 pollen from 9 surrounding patches in 0.5 seconds.
item.mine_swarm_simulator.scissors.desc: Collects ALL pollen from patch in front of you in 0.5 seconds.
item.mine_swarm_simulator.honey_dipper.d: Collects 2 pollen from 49 surrounding patches in 0.9 seconds.
item.mine_swarm_simulator.bubble_wand.de:
Collects 6 pollen from 16 patches in 0.75 seconds. Collects x2 from Blue flowers.
Every 10th swing spawns a Bubble somewhere on the field.
item.mine_swarm_simulator.scythe.desc:
Collects 7 pollen from a line 7 patches in 0.47 seconds. Collects x2 from Red flowers.
Every 20th swing spawns a Flame.
item.mine_swarm_simulator.golden_rake.de:
Collects 7 pollen from 4 lines of 4 patches in 0.6 seconds.
Every 5th scoop is supercharged to reach farther and collect more!
item.mine_swarm_simulator.spark_staff.de: Collects ALL pollen from the 3 tallest nearby flowers in 0.5 seconds and increases it by 20%.
item.mine_swarm_simulator.porcelain_dipp:
Collects 3 pollen from 49 patches in 0.7s, increasing white pollen by 50%.
Every 10th scoop summons a pillar of light that collects massive pollen!
item.mine_swarm_simulator.petal_wand.des:
Collects 6 pollen from 37 patches in 0.7s and boosts it by 100%.
Every 3rd swing fires a Petal Shuriken that causes bees to instantly convert pollen!
item.mine_swarm_simulator.dark_scythe.de: Harvest flames to unlock their Dark potential. Tend a violent field of violet fire to enhance your Super-Crit power and Red Ability Conversion.
item.mine_swarm_simulator.tide_popper.de: Pierce through flowers and bubbles with torrential waves. Ramps up the more you pop, then unleashes tidal waves in a violent surge. Splash Balloons with tall waves to earn Tide Blessing.
item.mine_swarm_simulator.gummyballer.de: Conjures up a delectable arsenal of gummy wrecking balls. Bombard Marks and Honey Tokens for massive gooey gains.
